info.author: Martin Owens
info.description:
This is Django Pile. It contains a pile of useful django pieces which django itself is currently missing.

These pieces have proven useful over a number of different and varied websites and the cost to maintaining multiple copies of them has reached a point where they need to be packaged on their own.

Please see the code for details in use.
